Package se.litsec.eidas.opensaml.ext.attributes

Interface EidasAttributeValueType

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BirthNameType, CurrentAddressType, CurrentFamilyNameType, CurrentGivenNameType, DateOfBirthType, GenderType, PersonIdentifierType, PlaceOfBirthType, TransliterationStringType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BirthNameTypeImpl, CurrentAddressTypeImpl, CurrentFamilyNameTypeImpl, CurrentGivenNameTypeImpl, DateOfBirthTypeImpl, GenderTypeImpl, PersonIdentifierTypeImpl, PlaceOfBirthTypeImpl, TransliterationStringTypeImpl
    public interface EidasAttributeValueType
    The bad decision of using dedicated XML types for each and every eIDAS attribute makes it hard for profiles that want to convert eIDAS attributes to their own definitions. This interface makes it somewhat easier to transform to and from string valued attributes.

    Martin Lindstr√∂m (martin.lindstrom@litsec.se)
